function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	local idPortal = Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorGizmo, "PORTAL")[1]
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idPortal)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	GIZMO_INARIUS_DOOR = idActorGizmo
	DOOR_AFTER_SCENE = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(GIZMO_INARIUS_DOOR, "DOORFLIP")[1]
		
	-- Slight delay, so the player sees the door open before the IGC starts.
	Hydra.Wait(3.0)
	
	-- Play IGC
	CampaignForcedPartyGatherPlayIGC(convInariusRTC, idActorPlayer)
	
	-- Wait some time before "closing the door" behind the player
	Hydra.ActorEnable(DOOR_AFTER_SCENE)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(GIZMO_INARIUS_DOOR)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.Wait(2.0)
	-- Player - "I should return to the Reverend Mother."
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorPlayer) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_PC_TO_PRAVA, idActorPlayer)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	idPriest = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Frac_Glacier2_Priest")[1]
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_PRIEST_01, idPriest)
end
